### Get transactions for a customer
GET http://localhost:5000/api/transactions/customer/<customer_id>

### Add credit transaction (Udhar Given)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customerId": "<customer_id>",
    "amount": 2500.50,
    "type": "give",
    "description": "Sold 5 bags of cement",
    "date": "2026-05-30T10:00:00Z"
}

### Add payment transaction (Paid Back)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customerId": "<customer_id>",
    "amount": 1000,
    "type": "take",
    "description": "Received partial cash payment",
    "date": "2026-05-31T09:00:00Z"
}

### Update transaction details
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/transactions/<transaction_id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 2800,
    "description": "Sold 5 bags of cement + 1 bag of sand"
}

### Delete a transaction
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/transactions/<transaction_id>
